<body>
  <div class="float-top-left hzi">
    <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm text-xs-center shrink">Back to<br>
      Bridging the Gap</a>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mb text-xs-center">
        <%= image_tag "teacher-conference.svg", class: "img-fluid" %>
      </div>
      <%= if notice.present? then alert_box notice, dismissible: true end %>
      <%= if alert.present? then alert_box alert, dismissible: true, context: :alert end %>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col col-sm-5 col-md-7">
          <p>You are invited to a PD day for secondary science teachers interested in STEM opportunities and industry engagement. <!-- This free conference features high profile keynote speaker, SA Chief Scientist Dr Leanna Read. --></p>
          <p><strong>Conference Details</strong></p>
          <p>Dr Carol Aldous, Project leader of the Bridging the Gap team will conduct a one-day conference for secondary school teachers and leaders interested in participating in the <a href="/">Bridging the Gap project</a>. Your attendance and possible willingness to mentor a student teacher would be very much appreciated.</p>
          <p>The conference will be of interest to those wanting to learn more about secondary education, industry engagement, and STEM.</p>
          <p>The conference will run on the 23rd of March 2018 from 9:00 AM. A free lunch will be provided. Please register your interest in the event below.</p>
          <p><strong>Topics</strong></p>
          <p>Topics covered in the course of the day will include:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Approaches to secondary science technology engineering and mathematics (STEM) education</li>
            <li>Secondary school and university STEM industry engagement</li>
            <li>Creative problem solving in science</li>
            <!-- <li>A tour of the new Flinders University Tonsley precinct (3D Printing, New Innovation)</li> -->
          </ul>
          <p><strong>Certification</strong></p>
          <p>6.5 hours of professional development - covering AITSL Standard 2, 3, 6 and 7.</p>
          <p>A certificate will be provided for each registered participant</p>
          <!-- <p class="text-xs-center"><a href="/documents/28" class="btn btn-primary">Conference Programme</a> <a href="/documents/27" class="btn btn-secondary">Conference Information</a> <a href="/calendar_anchor/2016/12/15/iCal-20161128-113901.ics" class="btn btn-secondary">Download Calendar Invite</a></p> -->
          <!-- <p><strong>Registration</strong></p>
          <p><em>Registration has now closed. Thank you for your interest in the Bridging the Gap project. We look forward to meeting you at the conference.</em></p> -->
         <%= form_tag("/register_for_teacher_conference", method: :post) do %>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="full_name">Full Name</label>
            <% if current_user.present?; name = current_user.name; email = current_user.email; else name = nil; email = nil; end %>
            <%= text_field_tag(:full_name, name, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Jane Doe") %>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <%= email_field_tag(:email, email, class: "form-control", placeholder: "jane.doe123@schools.sa.edu.au") %>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="role">Role</label>
            <%= text_field_tag(:role, @rsvp.role, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Science Teacher") %>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="school">School</label>
            <%= text_field_tag(:school, @rsvp.school, class: "form-control", placeholder: "My High School") %>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="year">Most Appropriate Year Level</label>
            <%= select_tag(:year_level, options_for_select([ "Year 7", "Year 8", "Year 9", "Year 10", "Year 11", "Year 12", "School Leadership Only" ], @rsvp.year_level), { selected: @rsvp.year_level, class: "form-control" } ) %>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group rfor">
            <label for="for_full_name">Registering For: Full Name</label>
            <%= text_field_tag(:for_full_name, @rsvp.for_full_name, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Jane Doe") %>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group rfor">
            <label for="for_email">Registering For: Email</label>
            <%= email_field_tag(:for_email, @rsvp.for_email, class: "form-control", placeholder: "john.doe123@schools.sa.edu.au") %>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group rfor">
            <label for="attending_too">Registering For: I wish to attend too</label> <br>
            <%= check_box_tag(:attending_too, @rsvp.attending_too) %>
          </div>
          <%= submit_tag "Register Interest", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-1 col-md-1"></div>
        <div class="col col-md-4">
          <p><strong>Venue &amp; Dates</strong></p>
          <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-1by1">
            <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3267.2283335099382!2d138.56955011537727!3d-35.02601728035221!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x6ab0d091d7a9f8ab%3A0x1f9164e0664c001d!2sCaf%C3%A9+Alere+%26+Alere+Function+Centre!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sau!4v1519169388045" class="embed-responsive-item"></iframe>
          </div>
          <br>
          <p><strong>Flinders University</strong></p>
          <p>Alere North</p>
          <p>Registry Road, Level 2 The Hub, Bedford Park SA 5042</p>
          <p><strong>Date</strong></p>
          <p>Monday, 23rd of March 2018</p>
          <p>09:00 AM &mdash; 3:30 PM</p>
          <br><br>
          <div class="text-xs-center">
            <%= image_tag "logo-on-white-with-letterhead-arb-print.png", class: "constrain-sm" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-xs-center">
      <br>
      <%= image_tag "dsd-flin.png", class: "constrain-sm" %>
      <br><br>
      <p class="small text-muted">&copy; 2017 Flinders University, All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </div>

    <script>
    $(".rfor").hide();

    $("#year_level").bind('change', function(e) {
      if ($(this).val() == "School Leadership Only") {
        $(".rfor").show();
      } else {
        $(".rfor").hide();
      }
    });
    </script>

  </body>
  </html>
